ir.mrmilad.utility

Class DateConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • ir.mrmilad.utility.DateConverter

  • public final class DateConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    DateConverter is a utility class for converting between dates of different calendars. This is carried out by various conversion methods provided by this class.
